### 2.4 Helper `aggregate_extraction()` (spécifique Panglot)

**Fichier :** `engine/src/learner_profile.rs` ou `engine/src/utils/aggregation.rs`

```rust
/// Helper pour agréger les sections d'un ExtractionResult
/// Spécifique à Panglot car nécessite les types concrets M et F
pub fn aggregate_extraction<M, F>(
    extraction: &ExtractionResult,
    morph_agg: &mut impl Aggregator<ExtractedFeature<M>>,
    seg_agg: &mut impl Aggregator<WordSegmentation<F>>,
) -> Result<(), ExtractionResultError>
where
    M: for<'de> serde::Deserialize<'de> + Aggregable,
    F: for<'de> serde::Deserialize<'de> + AggregableFields,
{
    // 1. Extraire la section "morphology"
    let morph: MorphSection<M> = extraction.get("morphology")?;

    // 2. Agréger target_features
    for feature in &morph.target_features {
        morph_agg.record(feature);
    }

    // 3. Agréger context_features
    for feature in &morph.context_features {
        morph_agg.record(feature);
    }

    // 4. Extraire et agréger "morpheme_segmentation" (si présent)
    if let Some(segs) = extraction.get::<Option<Vec<WordSegmentation<F>>>>("morpheme_segmentation")? {
        if let Some(segs) = segs {
            for seg in &segs {
                seg_agg.record(seg);
            }
        }
    }

    Ok(())
}
```

